

**Matt has masma wo bei g wechij doakag **

1 Heki am hu pi edgid ihda wechij doakag nam pi d pi ap chuꞌijkam ch pi ab hu kaiham g Jiosh. 2 Jijawul ha-geꞌejig o an em-uꞌukch hab masma mo an wehs ha uꞌukch hegam mo pi ab hu kaiham g Jiosh. Kum hegam ha oidch am hab e junihim ch ab s-wohog elid g ge Jiawul. 

3 Wehsijj ach hab wa masmakahim ch am hab junihim g hejel pi ap hab t-elida. K wa ab t-wui him g s-koꞌok t-namkidadag. 4-5 Pi ach wa ab hu wohog elid g Jiosh ch gam hu gawulkdas ab amjed heg hekaj pi ap t-chuꞌijig. K wabshaba g Jiosh t-hekaj si pihk e elid ch si s-hemajim t-doꞌibia ab amjed g t-chuꞌijig k ab t-mah g wechij doakag. Id o heg wa wepo mat heki hu ab i t-wuwhas muhkig t amjed 6 k am uhgk i t-uꞌu k an e-hugid an t-toa hab masma matsh hab juh g si e-alidag. Kuch hemu in melchud g Jesus kownaltalig jewed dahm hab masma mattsh an hahawa hab wo junihid dahm kahchim ch ed. 

7 Id at wehs am hab t-juni g Jiosh gahi wuhshanim g e-alidag. K hab d elidaj mat hab masma wehs am wo ha chehgi imhab i amjed mo has masma si s-hemajima ch ab si t-tatchua. 8 Ab at i s-t-hoꞌigeꞌel g Jiosh k doꞌibia natt pi ab i s-wohoch. Pi att wo shaꞌi t-nako machs hejel wo t-doꞌibia. Chum hems g t-wohochudadag o d mahkigdaj. 9 Pi o am hu haꞌichug machs haschukaj wo chum si t-gimaihunad no pi pi hejel hab d t-juni machs hekaj t-doꞌibia. 10 Ab at i t-mah g Jiosh ihda wechij doakag. Kuki hab d elidaj matt hekaj am hab wo junihid hegai s-ap chikpan mat heki hu am i apꞌech am t-wehhejed. 

**Nahnko mahs hemajkam o ab e hemakochudch ab s-wohochudch g Jesus **

11 Am g wo s-chegitok ahpim gawul mahs hemajkam mam has i masma mamt eda koi ab hu i s-wohoch g Christ. Pi am wa pahl hikuchkas hab masma mach ahchim Tutuligo. 12 K g Jiosh pi ab hu em-mahkch hegai mo haschu ab t-mahkch ch pi ab hu em-mahtchulid mat ia wo i wuhshad g e-alidag mat d wo si Kehshajk. Kum wa pi ab hu wui i e gewpkad g Jiosh 13-16 ch pi mahch ch pi edgid g chehanigaj. Kuch wa heg hekaj s-em-kehꞌid. M ahpim ab aigo hab waꞌap s-t-kehꞌid. K hegai t-kehꞌidadag hab sha masma mo g kolhai ch gam hu aꞌai t-gaꞌagwulkadch. T wabshaba g Christ s-ap am oidk hab e juh ihda chehanig k ab e muhkid kots t ab t-wehhejed k hab masma hugio g gewkdaj g chehanig. K heg pi ab hu hahawa t-chuꞌijigchud ahchim mach ab s-wohochud g Jiosh. Jesus Christ at ab i t-hemakoj e wehm. Kuch pi hahawa aꞌai s-t-kehꞌid nach pi d hahawa hemako. 

17 Pegih, ia at wa jiwia g Jiosh alidag jewed dahm k am ahgachug t-shahgid ihda doꞌibiadag ahga matt am hahawa em-wui uꞌapa ahpim gawul mahs hemajkam mam wa pi shaꞌi mahch g Jiosh. 18 K g Jiosh hab waꞌap ab em-mahkch g apꞌedag ahpim mamt hab waꞌap ab i s-wohochud k ab wui i e dagito. K hab waꞌap an em-uꞌukch g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag. 

19 Pi am d haha wabsh mehkjed oꞌodham ch wabshaba d aꞌaligaj g Jiosh. K g Jiosh ab em-mahkch g apꞌedag am e-kihdag ed hab masma mo ahchim ab t-mahkch. 20 Id o heg wa wepo mam d Jiosh kihta. Kuch heg wa wepo mach d kih shon ahchim mach haꞌi d Jesus si chuhchai ch haꞌi d Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam. K g Jesus an wehsijj t-uꞌukch hab masma mach an ab kihtas. 21 Am o wabsh kia geꞌedahim ihda kih no pi g Jiosh i ha baꞌihamahim hegam mo ab hahawa s-wohochud. 22 Kuch wehsijj t-wehm si s-ap hab chuꞌig ch d s-apꞌekam cheopi no pi g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag am t-eda. 

